OL,3,CPaul Pogba hit with four-year ban for
OL,4,Cdoping offence
OL,6,FIn December, anti-doping prosecutors
OL,7,Fin Italy suggested the 30-year-old
OL,8,Freceive a four-year ban, the maximum
OL,9,Fsentence a footballer can receive.
OL,11,FAccording to La Republicca, a court
OL,12,Fapproved the sentence on 29 February.
OL,14,FPogba has fought the allegations of
OL,15,Fdoping since his ban. He called for an
OL,16,Findependent counter-analysis of his
OL,17,Fdoping test, but those results also
OL,18,Fcame back positive.
