OL,3,CPaul Pogba hit with four-year ban for
OL,4,Cdoping offence
OL,6,FPogba also had the opportunity to make
OL,7,Fa plea bargain with the anti-doping
OL,8,Fagency, which could have resulted in a
OL,9,Flesser sentence.
OL,11,FInstead, he maintained his innocence
OL,12,Fand took the case to court where he
OL,13,Fwas eventually handed the ban.
OL,15,FHe reportedly plans to appeal the
OL,16,Fdecision.
